    public static enum AxionConfiguration.CharacterEncodingType
extends java.lang.Enum<AxionConfiguration.CharacterEncodingType>
    The character encoding type that an AxionConfiguration will use to read and write strings with the AxionInputStream.readString() and AxionOutputStream.writeString(String) methods.
    See Also:
    AxionConfiguration.setCharacterEncodingType(CharacterEncodingType)
